This incredible success was achieved thanks to a different ingredient than the one Mr. Obama had put forward.
Sixth Street is about analysis, practice, constant evaluation of ability and an exemplary attitude.
In addition, and here is an example that Mr. Obama could copy, reports Linda Mikels, principal of Sixth Street, the school has introduced the instruction of the English language "full immersion".
Total immersion in the English language focuses on the almost constant use of English in instruction.
