 According to us, more controls and inspections are needed, as is more intervention in the training of workers, and this from school".
- He added - "a further effort is needed in terms of communication and raising public awareness.
"But above all, a greater sense of responsibility on the part of employers is needed in the face of a phenomenon which represents a social emergency".
 Mercandelli then denounced the "progressive deterioration of the conditions for safeguarding the compensation provided for victims of work" and the "deviation of assistance towards which the system has been moving in recent years".
